Detailed Description

============================================================================

CSL CPTS API has common implementation for multiple SoCs along with below SoC specific implementation with the mapping as below.

  1. cpsw/V0 - SOC_K2K/SOC_K2H
  2. cpsw/V1 - SOC_K2E/SOC_K2L
  3. cpsw/V2 - SOC_K2G
  4. cpsw/V4 - SOC_C6678
  5. cpts/V0 - SOC_AM65XX
Note
: there may not be any ip specific implementation for that soc, if it contains only cslr_* files
